Saurin karuwa a cikin cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Kasashen da ke fama da cutar korona (COVID-19) suna nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, kuma Burtaniya ta bayyana cewa yayin da take cikin matakai daban-daban dangane da kowace ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Bisa ga gogewar Italiya, asibitoci da hukumomin kula da mutane ya kamata su kara kasancewa a shirye don karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 da za su bukaci kulawar lafiya da kuma kulawa mai mahimmanci.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton wani mutum da ke fama da cutar kumburi mai suna Ramrai, wanda ba a san asalinsa ba, a Wuhan, Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ruwaito cewa wata sabuwar nau'in coronavirus ce ta hanyar cutar coronavirus 2 ta hanyar cutar ta hanyar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta kasance ana kiranta cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Dalilin ya zuwa yanzu shine cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da wannan cutar mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar ta iska tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
Kashi 14 cikin 100 na COVID-19 sun zama na musamman da ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin 100 ke da ciwon da ke buƙatar kulawa sosai.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin karuwar cutar COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya da adadin cututtukan a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasuwancin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya.
Bayan mamaye kasar Sin, cutar COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma annobar COVID-19 da ke yaduwa a duniya a yanzu tana bin hanyar kasar Sin.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, babban darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya sanar da cewa COVID-19 cuta ce ta yaduwa.
A cikin Bayanai na 5 na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton COVID-19 da aka fara tabbatar da shi ta Turai dangane da yanayin cutar ta WHO.
A cikin kasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, Faransa ta fara bayar da rahoton sabbin mutane uku da aka tabbatar da su a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 ga mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Hubei, China.
