A Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC), an sabunta adadin adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duk faɗin duniya, daga tushe na hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, Hukumomin Lafiya na Kasa da na Yankin, da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya a kowace rana a 8:00 am.
Duk waɗannan bayanan ana amfani dasu don kimanta cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, kuma ana kwatanta duk waɗannan bayanan da bayanan Italiya.
A matsayin wakilin cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa jerin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 da suka kwantar da hankali a cikin kwanaki 14 dangane da yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna karuwar adadin shari'o'in da aka samu a kowace ƙasa da aka sanar a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
