Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasar tana da albarkatu fiye da ko ƙasa da Italiya (wani matsakaici na wurare 12.5 don kulawa da gado don mutane 100,000 a shekara ta 2010-11).
An bayar da samfurin da ya shafi rashin iyawar kiwon lafiya a cikin sabon sabon kimantaccen haɗarin COVID-19 na shida na ECDC, tare da kimantawa ga ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya cewa yawan masu cutar COVID-19 suna da haɗari fiye da yadda za a iya ba da gadon kulawa mai tsanani &gt; 90%.
Saboda da yawa daga cikin lokuta sun faru, suna tattare a wasu yankuna a cikin ƙasashen Turai, Yammacin Turai da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa suna yawanci kawai bauta wa yawan mutanen yankin da aka ƙayyade, don haka ya kamata a ba da bayani game da shari'o'i da kuma yanayin kula da kulawa a ƙarƙashin Sashin Gida na Cibiyar Kula da Yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 ta duniya tana tasowa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a kula da ƙasashe, asibitoci da hukumomin kulawa da su don su kasance a shirye don sabon yanayin watsawar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa al'umma da ke faruwa a cikin sauri da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya da kuma musamman kulawa mai mahimmanci kamar yadda lamarin yake faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon saurin kimanta hadarin ECDC, saurin amsawa mai dacewa da kuma cikakkiyar hanya tana da mahimmanci a jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2-virus, tare da sauyawa daga juriya zuwa hanyoyin ragewa, yayin da saurin karuwa a cikin adadin lokuta bazai ba masu ɗaukar shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don gano karɓa da amsa yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da shi ba da wuri.
Ƙididdigar haɗarin haɗari mai sauri ta kuma gabatar da matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai gajeren lokaci da za a samu a yayin da kasashe ke da damar kara inganta kokarin su na hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba a kan hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, tsarin kula da lafiyar kasashen Turai da na sauran kasashen Turai na iya fuskantar karuwar marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin 'yan kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) da ta haifar da cutar sankarar cuta ta hanyar numfashi (SARS) ta hanyar cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ya zuwa yanzu ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 da kamuwa da cutar sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana kama da kwayar cutar, wanda ke da nasa fasalin guda daya, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS a kan dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003. SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar daga tsutsotsi kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar daukar hoto kamar SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan haɗari da ƙarancin mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da yawa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, maza kuma suna da yawa fiye da mata.
Don amsa yawan wallafe-wallafen da ke gudana a kan cutar da ke yaduwa, wannan labarin yana son samar da cikakken bayani game da batutuwan bincike da ke ci gaba da sauri.
Za mu tattauna game da cututtuka, abubuwan da ke haifar da cututtuka, ilimin lissafi, bincike, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cututtuka.
Duk da cewa akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka mana mu gano kuma mu magance wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin hutun bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin mamaki da ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba ga duk 'yan kasar Sin da aka ba da shawarar su kasance a gida don hutu da kuma makonni bayan barkewar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV), wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a cikin 2003. Saboda haka, an sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma sauran cututtukan da suka shafi an sake masa suna COVID-19 (COVID-19).
An fara barkewar cutar ne a birnin Wuhan, China, tare da yaduwar cutar a cikin ƙasa da kuma zuwa kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 guda 80000 inda aka sallami marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 kuma an kashe marasa lafiya sama da 3000.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce babbar magabcin jama'a kuma tana da matukar tasiri fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, an wallafa fiye da 200 na binciken COVID-19 da suka hada da nazarin cutar, kamuwa da cuta, ganewa da magani tun daga farkon rahoton da aka bayar a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya gano jerin cututtukan da ke ware daga marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita yanayin bincike a cikin sabbin fannoni masu tasowa da sauri.
