A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da hukumar tsakiya ta yanke game da aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa yayin da ba shawarar da WHO ta bayar ba ce, amma kuma muhimmin nunawa ne na sadaukarwa don magance cutar a wuraren da cutar ta fi taruwa, kuma ya kira cutar cutar "ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da cewa an yi kamuwa da cutar daga mutane zuwa mutane a waje da China da kuma karuwar wannan adadin a wasu ƙasashe biyar, WHO ta bayyana wannan annobar a matsayin farkon annobar cutar ta duniya ta farko da za a iya amfani da ita a lokacin da ake kira ICES (PICES).
Babban daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce, PHEIC na da haɗarin yaduwa a duniya, musamman ga ƙasashe masu karamin da matsakaitan kudade, ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
"A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa ""babu wani dalili ga matakan da za su hana ba dole ba tafiya da cinikayya ta kasa da kasa"" kuma ""World Health Organization ba ta bada shawarar yin iyakance cinikayya da ƙaura""".
"A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi kira ga al'umma ta duniya da ta ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don samar da kudade don shirye-shiryen dabaru a cikin ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan kuɗaɗe, ta ba da shawarar gaggawa don tallafawa waɗancan ƙasashen da ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, duk da cewa an yi ta".
"Tedros ya kara da cewa, ""dukan al'ummai idan akwai matalauta, suna da daidaito ga matalauta"" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar kasa da kasa da "kasuwanci a yau ba zai rasa fiye da haka ba a nan gaba". A wani taron manema labarai a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta kira cutar COVID-19".
