ACE ta hanyar rage hormone testosterone I zuwa jini, hormone testosterone II.
ACE2 ya raba amino acid carboxyl-terminal amino acid daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya raba shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
