ACE2 yana taimakawa wajen rage yawan amino acid mai karɓar SLC6A19 da aka gani a cikin cutar Hartnup.
Saboda ƙwayoyin cuta na ACE2 suna taka rawa a matsayin babban tashar shiga cikin kwayoyin halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus wanda ke haifar da SARS) da SARS-CoV-2 (virus wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Har ila yau, an bayyana cewa, karɓar S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa cikin ACE2 enzymes da ke kan kwayoyin halitta, wanda sakamakon haka ya haifar da rarrabuwa da kuma sanya kwayoyin cutar da enzymes a cikin endosomes na kwayoyin halitta.
