Ana daukar daukar nauyin maganin rigakafi da aka yi amfani da shi da kuma gina jiki wanda ya warke daga COVID-19 ga mutanen da ke bukatarsa a matsayin hanyar yin allurar rigakafi ba tare da yin allurar ba.
An gwada wannan dabarar don SARS tare da sakamako mai ban mamaki.
Kwayar cuta ita ce tsarin aikin da ake tsammani maganin antibacterial zai iya daidaitawa, daidaita kariya daga SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, akwai wasu hanyoyin da za a iya yin su, kamar su cytokines, ƙwayoyin da ke dogara da antibodies da/ko phagocytosis.
Alal misali, wani nau'i na maganin rigakafi na rashin aiki da aka yi da kwayoyin halitta masu ƙonewa suna cikin ci gaba.
Aikin samar da jini na masu warkewa daga cutar yana dauke da wani abu da ke dauke da wani nau'i na maganin cutar da za a sake kirkira.
Cutar korona ta ƙunshi wasu nau'ikan cututtuka da ke da alaƙa da juna.
Li Wenliang, likitan asibitin Wuhan, wanda daga baya ya kamu da cutar kuma ya mutu daga COVID-19 bayan ya sanar da sanin yadda cutar ke yaduwa.
